Two surgical edits to the hero. Both are ADDITIVE — keep the existing
className strings; add cream-only classes that no-op outside the wrapper.

  EDIT A: Replace the inline radial-gradient with CSS-variable references
          so cream's --hero-glow-* tokens override the orange/navy/pink.
  EDIT B: Add `boxed-word` class to the "without writing prompts" span.
          Inside .theme-cream this becomes a chunky terracotta box with
          a -2° rotation. Outside (which doesn't apply for this component
          since it's marketing-only), nothing changes.

