OUTPUT BEHAVIOR:
- Navy (no .theme-cream wrapper, e.g. via direct import elsewhere):
    "without writing prompts." renders as orange text-accent (current look)
- Cream (wrapped in MarketingLayout / .theme-cream):
    "without writing prompts." renders as a chunky terracotta box with a
    cocoa border, white text, slight -2° rotation, and a 6px hard shadow.

If the rotated box is too playful for your taste, edit the
`.theme-cream .boxed-word` block in app/app.css to remove `transform: rotate(-2deg)`.
